long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This tool stores a vector representation of your browsing history created using OpenAI's embedding model. It will be used for Max's research project on whether this model is able to predict real life relationships by comparing vector representations of browser history.
